<li>5th-<Link to="/spell/cone_of_cold">cone of cold</Link><sup><InnerLink showBacklink="backlink-eq-spellbook-arctic_call-ref-S-3" id="eq-spellbook-arctic_call-ref-S-3" data-hash-target to="eq-spellbook-arctic_call-S">1</InnerLink></sup>, <Link to="/spell/mages_private_sanctum">mage's private sanctum</Link>, <Link to="/spell/permanency">permanency</Link>, <Link to="/spell/teleport">teleport</Link>, <Link to="/spell/wall_of_force">wall of force</Link><sup><InnerLink showBacklink="backlink-eq-spellbook-arctic_call-ref-S-4" id="eq-spellbook-arctic_call-ref-S-4" data-hash-target to="eq-spellbook-arctic_call-S">1</InnerLink></sup></li>
