<li>3rd-<Link to="/spell/cloak_of_winds">cloak of winds</Link>, <em>explosive runes,</em> <Link to="/spell/haste">haste</Link>, <Link to="/spell/lightning_bolt">lightning bolt</Link>, <Link to="/spell/nondetection">nondetection</Link>, <Link to="/spell/twilight_knife">twilight knife</Link></li>
