<li>7th-<Link to="/spell/artificers_curse">artificer's curse</Link>, <Link to="/spell/control_construct">control construct</Link>, <Link to="/spell/emblem_of_greed">emblem of greed</Link>, <Link to="/spell/firebrand">firebrand</Link>, <Link to="/spell/greater_age_resistance">greater age resistance</Link>, <Link to="/spell/greater_teleport">greater teleport</Link>, <Link to="/spell/legendary_proportions">legendary proportions</Link>, <Link to="/spell/reverse_gravity">reverse gravity</Link></li>
