<li>1st-<Link to="/spell/expeditious_construction">expeditious construction</Link>, <Link to="/spell/identify">identify</Link>, <Link to="/spell/magic_weapon">magic weapon</Link>, <Link to="/spell/mirror_strike">mirror strike</Link>, <Link to="/spell/protection_from_evil">protection from evil</Link>, <Link to="/spell/unerring_weapon">unerring weapon</Link></li>
